data.description: Beautiful, very well maintained and remodeled home located near historic Downtown Paragould! There are so many amenities to mention in this home.  The most notable is the large in ground swimming pool with a covered patio near to stay cool and covered. The kitchen has been remodeled with bright new cabinets, countertops, backsplash and sink.  The main level of the home features 3 large bedrooms with ample closet space with built in shelving. The foyer is grand and inviting and welcomes you into the large living room with gas log fireplace.  Upstairs is a completely new and finished out large bedroom and walk in closest.
